Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari's got a 250?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have fun next time we go touring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dad's pretty lenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it on condition that she helps her father carrying out deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Delivering sushi with a 250??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like all that nigiri is gonna be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just going to turn into chirashi in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, what a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away with this just with an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving around like crazy while carrying goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember raising my daughter like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of father attacks his own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I ought to spank your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you're too vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As your punishment, I'm going to keep the key to your bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, how did you grow up to be so ill-mannered?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what does he expect from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... My dad won't listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask again once he's in a better mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take at least a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you just go without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate doing things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't like acting sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true you can't go touring with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite saying all that, I've still got to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going way too fast,\Nespecially for a beginner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! If something happens to you,\Nyour dad's gonna chew us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you're responsible for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a very popular guy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more annoying than helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko! That's enough already! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that guy isn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so. That punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know bikes aren't that dangerous\Nas long as you follow the regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the way she acts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut her some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People tend to act reckless when they're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes doing things\Nbehind their parent's backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember being like that once too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I've done things I regret now\Nwithout even realizing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Being worried is part of a parent's job, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't anyone following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get past!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick too close or you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Hiroko, have you grown bigger again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NLooks like I'll have to get a new bra soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you eat to get that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about what you eat, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think about Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi? He's just an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the kind of guy I'd want as a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guys do you like then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Kei, we shouldn't be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! A chance like this doesn't come often!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroko's going to break up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A temporary breakup or nude girls,\Nwhich do you care about more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,N-nude girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought you'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who rode the bike with this thing on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Only Sho can notice these kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Blatantly peeking on girls is dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that better than doing it sneakily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's sneaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That's right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People who peek on others are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen at the spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my amulet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait! I'll definitely get it back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, wait! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing from those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They were watching!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early for a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Step it up, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, these guys are pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, you've got some skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing much. Just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, are you happy now? Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a marriage amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold onto this until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nabeshima{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is about helping you make more money, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big words from a guy who likes to play around with said money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing that connects us as father and son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a witty retort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nyou're entering the next race, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I refused,\Nwouldn't you just force me to enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're driving our latest model.\NIt'd be a shame if you didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A victory for me will raise\Nour popularity in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how good it is, the machine won't win the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,1969.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,17 years old, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad's pissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. he took away the key as usual,\Nbut he was grateful to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've gained some respect from him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually was wondering if he\Nshould ask you to become his son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go change the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A cheque?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Three million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my get-well present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chump change for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just settle this with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of money, just give back Mariko's amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not forget basic manners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And secondly, this amount of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nabeshima Mitsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a model\Nthat was discontinued 7 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from that incident, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The controversy is starting to wear off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to start producing them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who caused\Nthe accident was Nagase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Raita Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once known as the genius "Bullet Rider".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... "Bullet Rider" Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks to that accident\Nwe found out what was wrong with the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it wasn't the driver's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops, I didn't mean to say that!\NJust forget about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a mistake on the driver's part...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirou sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped him at cleaning too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost like a dedicated wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A white Supra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like my prayers were answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know about Raita Nagase's past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Raita's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he quit driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit... driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He got scared. Turned into a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You always get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Raita's not that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to check out\Nwhether I'm lying or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know the true face of Raita Nagase...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get killed by him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirou! Mariko got taken away by that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta tell her father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait! Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we should call master instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go find Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Projector Room{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 23 is Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who tried to dodge Nagase\Nwas taken to a hospital, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But... In that situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good friend of Nagase's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's infuriating is that after the incident\NNagase never took part in a race again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who lost his life by dodging him died for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He became afraid after seeing his friend die before his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quitting racing is Raita's way of taking responsibility for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any right to judge that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, you morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Mariko back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to lay a finger on her!\NI'll beat you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fallen for her?\NThis idiot never ceases to amuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Mariko out of here no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice show you've put up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,0:24:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sho! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Raita...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko! Keiichi! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.40,0:24:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.30,0:24:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my no-good son has been causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.10,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Mr. Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.10,0:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like parents who get involved in their kids fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.50,0:24:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who should be apologizing\Nis not you, but this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't bow my head for people weaker than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need to get better?\NI have to win against you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it. miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You ride bikes too, am I correct?\NLet's settle this with a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.20,0:25:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nabeshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've reserved Harumi Circuit for a day one month from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.10,0:25:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a 1 on 1 race there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A race?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.70,0:25:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the former racing legend on her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.70,0:25:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.90,0:25:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.70,0:25:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari! This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.90,0:25:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is enter?\NAnd win the race?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.90,0:25:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.30,0:26:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A race, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.30,0:26:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We kind of had an agreement, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.80,0:26:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.80,0:26:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really ask for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.90,0:26:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to fool me! I won't allow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.90,0:26:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.90,0:26:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we need to talk about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.90,0:26:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...\NI need to race against him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.80,0:26:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose. Not to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.20,0:27:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick too close or you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always told me to never run away\Nfrom a fight, ever since I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't some quarrel between kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.70,0:27:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.70,0:27:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last time, no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.10,0:27:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Okazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.30,0:28:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, the situation being what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.30,0:28:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Please teach Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.30,0:28:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happened to her,\Nmy wife would never forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.30,0:29:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.30,0:29:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your owner's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.80,0:29:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A real race machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.30,0:29:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I used to drive back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's made for racing,\Nit's lighter than your bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.50,0:29:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shift up and down are reversed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I'm riding?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.50,0:29:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's no good this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.50,0:30:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn it into a special bike\Nborrowing my friend's engineering skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.50,0:30:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.50,0:30:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.50,0:30:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.50,0:30:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.50,0:30:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do well in racing just with ordinary physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.50,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do some serious training.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.10,0:30:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one month. It's gonna be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.10,0:30:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.10,0:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this covering?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.10,0:31:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this wheel! It's all solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.50,0:31:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of machine is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.50,0:32:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.50,0:32:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the special bike, Boomerang!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.50,0:33:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten pretty muscular lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.70,0:33:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would anyone want to still marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.20,0:33:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wansuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.70,0:33:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.00,0:33:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.30,0:33:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.50,0:33:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd tell you after the race, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it could be too late by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.00,0:34:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a kid...\NI've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.50,0:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.00,0:34:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko? Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Raita?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.30,0:34:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.10,0:34:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you start riding bikes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.10,0:34:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.60,0:34:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:35:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing with my bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.10,0:35:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The bike alone won't win you the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.10,0:35:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I wouldn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.10,0:35:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If this test drive goes well,\Nwe need to start producing those bikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.10,0:35:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If it's your son,\Neverything should go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.30,0:35:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.30,0:35:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tolerated his stupid behavior\Nand always covered for him for this day's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.60,0:35:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.30,0:35:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NI've never seen a bike like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.60,0:36:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?\NThis is the bike you rode 7 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.00,0:36:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as bad as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time the faulty parts have been fixed, Mr. Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.50,0:36:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was defective?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.50,0:37:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How many laps are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.40,0:37:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.10,0:37:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You came, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.60,0:37:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,4 laps. Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.60,0:37:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.60,0:37:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.60,0:37:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast! He's not just some spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.90,0:37:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi! He came after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.30,0:37:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagase built quite a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.70,0:38:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His past experience as a rider sure shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.30,0:38:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?\NI'm talking about the design, not the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That would become a top seller for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.70,0:38:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll start gathering information about it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.50,0:38:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.70,0:38:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.70,0:38:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell down...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.70,0:38:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.30,0:38:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? To stop the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't win! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.70,0:39:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love her, then believe in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.70,0:39:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! We found out who designed the bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.50,0:39:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Nagase's friend's company...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.10,0:39:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boomerang?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.10,0:40:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.10,0:40:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.70,0:40:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing great again!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.70,0:40:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Mariko! It's the final lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.70,0:40:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.50,0:40:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Dad...\NWatch over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.50,0:41:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She's getting too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.70,0:41:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!! She won!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.70,0:41:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely something...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.70,0:41:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!! Amazing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.00,0:41:53.40,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,We only met for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:58.60,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It was too late by then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.00,0:41:53.40,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Deau no ga sukoshi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:58.60,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Ososugita dake nanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.60,0:42:09.90,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Mou anata ni chikazuku no mo dekinainowa naze
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.60,0:42:09.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why cannot I be close to you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.50,0:42:22.90,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Hashagisugita kisetsu ga kaze no you ni sugiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.40,0:42:35.90,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Ii yatsu nante dokonidemo iru nante itta mama
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.10,0:42:48.00,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Anata ga koe wo kaketa sei yo
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:59.90,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Mune ga itamu no mo, otona ni naru no mo
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.20,0:43:12.50,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Sono te wo nigirishimeta mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:20.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Saigo ni hitokoto iwasete
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.00,0:43:24.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,I still love you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:57.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Deau no ga sukoshi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:02.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Ososugita dake nanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.50,0:44:14.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Mou kono mama ano hito wo oinukenai no ne
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.70,0:44:27.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Tokei no hari wa itsumo wakare wo kizamu dake
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.40,0:44:41.70,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Shiawase nante dokonidemo aru nante uso nano
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.50,0:42:22.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The passing season disappeared like the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.40,0:42:35.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Even though I said good people can be found anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.10,0:42:48.00,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because you called out to me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:59.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I felt a pain in my heart, and grew more mature
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.20,0:43:12.50,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Holding your hand tightly
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:20.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let me say one last thing to you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:57.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,We only met for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:02.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It was too late by then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.50,0:44:14.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I cannot catch up with you anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.70,0:44:27.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The hand of the clock always seems to tick towards the time of parting
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.40,0:44:41.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It's a lie that happiness can be found anywhere
